name: Homies 3D - Character and Icon Set
description: Homies 3D is a set of cute and fashionable 3D character constructor and icon library. Created with designers in mind, Homies helps you step up your design project with beautiful 3D assets and changeable colors. High resolution 3D renders are packed together in a Figma project file to easily integrate in your project directly. Grab your sample character and use it directly in your project right away! More info at homies3d.com
